OwayenguNgqongqoshe weziMali noMnyango wezaseKhaya uMnuz Malusi Gigaba utshele iKhomishana ephenya ngokuLawulwa koMbuso yiDlanzana, ukuthi umshado wabo omhlophe wakhokhelwa owayengunkosikazi wakhe uNorma Mngoma. Uthe umshado wabo wakhokhelwa  uMngoma, ngakho lezi zigidi athi bazinikwa abakwaGupta kungenzeka ukuthi uyena owanikezwa zona. “Ngangazi ukuthi yena unemali. Kwakungumsebenzi womndeni wakhe ukukhokhela umshado wethu omhlophe. Ngakhokhela amasudi ami, abakhaphi bami bakhokhela amasudi abo ngoba bengixhasa. Uma ethi umshado waba u-R4 kuya ku-R5 million kusho ukuthi kwaba imali yakhe leyo. Mina ngakhokhela umshado wesintu owawusekhaya,” kusho uGigaba. Uthe akaze amukele ngisho nesenti kwabakaGupta. UGigaba uthe usola abathize bezepolitiki abasebenzisa owayengunkosikazi wakhe ukumcindezela kwezepolitiki. Uthe unkosikazi wakhe uNksz Norma Mngoma wayeke amxoxele ngabanye abantu bezepoilitiki abebemfaka ingcindezi yokuthi akenze isitatimende, wathi kodwa uMngoma wayemthembisile ukuthi uyobeka umndeni wakhe phambili. “UMngoma washo kimina ukuthi ufakelwa ingcindezi, abanye abantu abakwipolitiki ukuba azofaka isitatimende. Bathi bafuna ukuqeda ngami kwezepolitiki. Wathi yena uzothola imali nezinye izinto. Washo yena izinto ayezohlomula ngazo uma efakaza ngami. Wayelokhu ethi ngeke akuvume lokho. Wathi uzobeka umndeni wakhe phambili, kodwa wagcina ezile ezofakaza. Kulezi zitatimende zakhe, kuningi okuphikisanayo okukhomba ukuthi akuyona into esuka kuye.Okunye kusuka kwimibiko yabezindaba,” kusho uGigaba. UGigaba uthe uMngoma uhubhuza amanga uma ethi wayethatha imiyalelo kuMyeni no -Ajay Gupta. “Azikho zinto engingathi uNkk Dudu Myeni wayezidlulisa zisuka kowayenguMengameli uJacob Zuma, ziza kimina. Nganginethimba lami engangilithinta uma ngidinga ukuxhumana noMengameli. Ayikho into uZuma ayeyitshela uMyeni, bese (uMyeni) eyidlulisela kimina. Uma uZuma wayedinga ukukhuluma nami wayengasho uma kunemihlangano yekhabhinethi,” kusho uGigaba. USihlalo wekhomishini iJaji Raymond Zondo ubuze ukuthi uma kuyinto engekho yini pho eyenza washo lezi zinto unkosikazi wakhe. Echaza uGigaba uthe, uMngoma wayeqikelela ukuthi uma efakaza akazifaki yena njengoba ayethi wayenikwa imali kodwa akaze abone ngqo uGigaba enikezwa esandleni, kodwa wayevele abone isikhwama sakhe uGigaba sesinensavunsavu yemali. “Ikhomishini kade yaba khona ngo-2018, wayengasiboni isidingo sokuba eze. Uze wafuna ukuza manje, ngoba sekunesigigaba  sokulimala kwemoto emzini wami. “Ngangiwungqongqoshe ngihola, ngeke ngazi kahle izinhloso zakhe ngaphandle kokuthi okwenza athi akazi ngemali ingoba akafuni ukuzifaka. “Ebhuthini lami angikaze ngibone imali. Isikhwama sami sincane kabi, asiphathi ngisho nemali edlula ku-R5 000,” kusho uGigaba. Uthe uMngoma nje umuntu onamanga kabi ngoba waqamba amanga nangoyise ayethi ucebile. Ngaphambilini uGigaba watshela ikhomishini ukuthi yena wayazi ukuthi uyise kaMngoma owayehlala eNew York washona, wamshiyela imali eningi, kepha wagcina ethola ukuthi lowo baba kwakungumuntu ayezoshada naye.  